Class TestingObjectManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.mlaursen.database.managers.ObjectManager
      • com.github.mlaursen.database.managers.TestingObjectManager

  • public class TestingObjectManager
extends ObjectManager
    This is an extension of the Object Manager. The main difference is that it is using a TestingConnectionManager versus the connection manager.
    Author:
    mlaursen
